  "body": "We have seen inefficiency when we `process_slot` due to `hash_tree_root(state)` is slow but the only item changed in the state is `slot`. It wouldn't be that slow with proper caching branches of the state tree structure. This issue tracks how we can improve. We've seen multiple incidents where RPC context times out due to slowness of `process_slot`",
